<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Students who have earned a score of 4 or higher on an Advanced Placement exam may receive advanced credit. Credit will be awarded for courses in which the content parallels Montserrat's own program of study. The official AP score report from the College Board should be included with your application. Montserrat is identified with the College Board code 9101.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.montserrat.edu/admissions/all-applicants.php" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
